.block-slider-tab.hidden-xs
  .container
    #carousel-main-tab.carousel.slide(data-ride='carousel')
       ol.carousel-indicators

          li.active.animated-down-0-7s(data-target='#carousel-main-tab', data-slide-to='0')
             .block-slider-tab-wrap-img
               img.svg(src="../img/home/reduce-energy-icon.svg" alt="")
             h4.block-slider-tab-title Reduce Energy
               br
               | Costs

          li.animated-down-0-7s(data-target='#carousel-main-tab', data-slide-to='1')
             .block-slider-tab-wrap-img
                img.svg(src="../img/home/recover-icon.svg" alt="")
             h4.block-slider-tab-title.animated-down-0-8s Recover System
              br
              | Capacity

          li.animate-40(data-target='#carousel-main-tab', data-slide-to='2')
             .block-slider-tab-wrap-img
               img.svg(src="../img/home/reduce-maintenance-icon.svg" alt="")
             h4.block-slider-tab-title Reduce
               br
               | Maintenance

          li.animate-40(data-target='#carousel-main-tab', data-slide-to='3')
            .block-slider-tab-wrap-img
              img.svg(src="../img/home/improve-icon.svg" alt="")
            h4.block-slider-tab-title Improve Comfort
              br
              | For Tenants

          li.animate-40(data-target='#carousel-main-tab', data-slide-to='4')
            .block-slider-tab-wrap-img
              img.svg(src="../img/home/lowest-icon.svg" alt="")
            h4.block-slider-tab-title Lowest Total Cost
              br
              | Of Ownership

       .carousel-inner.animate-40(role='listbox')
          .item.active
             .text-center
                p.content-text The DeltaPValve® uses far less energy by increasing system stability. In fact, it has proven to reduce energy consumption in heating and cooling systems by 20 - 40%. This translates to saving millions of dollars in operating costs and eliminates needless environmental waste.
          .carousel-caption
          - for(x=0; x<=5; x++)
            .item
               .text-center
                  p.content-text The DeltaPValve® helps achieve maximum efficiency for heating and cooling systems. By using the existing system more effectively, the building can recover lost capacity and often times defer the need for costly expansion projects.
            .item
              .text-center
                  p.content-text The DeltaPValve® is industrial quality and designed to last the life of the facility and comes with an industry-leading 10-year warranty. Each DeltaPValve® is self-balancing, therefore eliminating the need for repeated system commissioning. This means the cost of maintaining system performance after installation is significantly reduced.
            .item
              .text-center
                  p.content-text The DeltaPValve® tightens control within heating and cooling systems, enabling precise response and the stabilization of leaving air temperature. This improves comfort for tenants and reduces the number of hot and cold calls received by the maintenance team.
            .item
              .text-center
                  p.content-text By reducing energy costs, delivering optimum system capacity, and minimizing maintenance, the DeltaPValve® simply delivers a lower total cost of ownership than any other flow control product on the market.
